        <mxCell id="xELkamH10cSAUg8blqq6-60" value="&lt;i&gt;if training neural nets from scratch, choice of tokenizer could also have a major impact&lt;/i&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=6;spacingRight=6;fontColor=#D6B656;" vertex="1" parent="1">
